        "reaction_type": "加氢转化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydroconversion reaction",
        "description": "在固定床流动反应器中，使用NiMo/USY@Al-SBA-15催化剂，在380°C、3.0MPa条件下，将废食用油（WCO）与环己烷的溶液（20wt%）进行加氢转化，生产生物航空燃料（C9-C15烃类）。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydroconversion of WCO was conducted in a fixed-bed flow reactor (1.2cm i.d. and 45cm in length). The reaction temperature was controlled by three thermocouples on the reactor wall and monitored with a thermocouple in the catalyst bed. To achieve a sufficient catalyst bed length in the reactor, 8g of catalyst was loaded and fixed by SiC. A solution of 20wt% WCO in cyclohexane was used as feedstock and supplied at a flow rate of 0.8mLmin–1 with a high-pressure pump.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
